 "content": "CNN translated:\n\n1. White man = Black man\n2. Terror attack against Mamdani = ISIS attack, definitely not against Mamdani\n3. Woman = Man\n4. Intense debate prep = Napping by the pool\n\nThis is CNN.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2320}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASGEDliOR", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 40, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "maga", "id": 8481533, "raw_content": "Trump, I'd like for you to announce a loss in confidence in Thune.  This needs to trigger to the people and to senate that we need a new leader, one who can work with you to get a MAGA agenda pushed through.  The senate turned their back on you when they elected Thune, and Thune turned his back on you when he wouldn't let senate recess.\n\nSenate needs new leadership.  And it is easy, there just needs to be a new election for senate leader, and the new leader only needs 26 votes to become leader.\n\nI don't care if it splinters the R party, they are already a mess.  Nothing is going to happen unless they pass the SAVE America act, and it looks like Thune doesn't even want to try.  This makes him completely ineffective as leader, and he needs to leave that position.", "author": "Trump-16-20-24-28-32", "created": 1773247542071, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Trump-16-20-24-28-32", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Senate, you need to elect a new senate leader, there is a loss in confidence in Thune.  As long as Thune is the senate leader, you are going to be at a stand still.", "last_comment_created": 1773254101398, "content": "<p>Trump, I'd like for you to announce a loss in confidence in Thune.  This needs to trigger to the people and to senate that we need a new leader, one who can work with you to get a MAGA agenda pushed through.  The senate turned their back on you when they elected Thune, and Thune turned his back on you when he wouldn't let senate recess.</p>\n<p>Senate needs new leadership.  And it is easy, there just needs to be a new election for senate leader, and the new leader only needs 26 votes to become leader.</p>\n<p>I don't care if it splinters the R party, they are already a mess.  Nothing is going to happen unless they pass the SAVE America act, and it looks like Thune doesn't even want to try.  This makes him completely ineffective as leader, and he needs to leave that position.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 40, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\u00a0\u00a0AMERICA\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0FIRST\u00a0", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASGEDlRTg", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 44, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8481454, "raw_content": "", "author": "flp999", "created": 1773245592808, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "blockchain-the-vote", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASGEDlRTg.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/MQn1m5v3Y57m.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/4yocBon23bBiugHm.jpeg", "width": 279, "content